2013 [[Tor N\u00f8rretranders]], Danish science author\n*[[July 1]]\n**[[Candia McWilliam]], Scottish fiction writer\n**[[Lisa Scottoline]], American writer of legal thrillers\n*[[July 5]]\n**[[Sebastian Barry]], Irish novelist, playwright and poet\n**[[Mia Couto]] (Ant\u00f3nio Em\u00edlio Leite Couto), Mozambican fiction writer and poet\n*[[July 6]]\n**[[Michael Boyd (theatre director)|Michael Boyd]], British theatre director\n**[[William Wall (writer)|William Wall]], Irish author and poet\n*[[July 12]] \u2013 [[Robin Robertson]], Scottish-born poet, novelist and editor\n*[[August 2]] \u2013 [[Caleb Carr]], American writer\n*[[August 7]] \u2013 [[Vladimir Sorokin]], Russian writer\n*[[August 8]] \u2013 [[Iain Pears]], English writer\n*[[September 6]] \u2013 [[Raymond Benson]], American novelist\n*[[September 13]] \u2013 [[Hiromi It\u014d]] (\u4f0a\u85e4 \u6bd4\u5442\u7f8e), Japanese poet, essayist and translator\n*[[October 19]] \u2013 [[Jason Shinder]], American poet and editor (died [[2008 in literature|2008]])\n*[[November 12]] \u2013 [[Katharine Weber]], American author and academic\n*[[November 23]] \u2013 [[Steven Brust]], American fantasy author\n*[[December 28]] \u2013 [[Liu Xiaobo]] (\u5218\u6653\u6ce2), Chinese critic, writer and activist (died [[2017 in literature|2017]])\n\n''Uncertain dates''\n*[[Wang Xiaoni]] (\u738b\u5c0f\u59ae), Chinese poet\n*[[Regina Yaou]], Ivorienne novelist (died 2017)\n\n==Deaths==\n*[[January 20]] \u2013 [[Robert P. Tristram Coffin]], American poet, essayist and novelist (born [[1892 in literature|1892]])\n*[[February 23]] \u2013 [[Paul Claudel]], French poet, dramatist and diplomat (born [[1868 in literature|1868]])\n*[[April 10]] \u2013 [[Pierre Teilhard de Chardin]], French philosopher and essayist (born [[1881 in literature|1881]])\n*[[May 16]] \u2013 [[James Agee]], American writer (born [[1909 in literature|1909]])\n*[[June 6]] \u2013 [[Joseph Jefferson Farjeon]], English crime writer (born [[1883 in literature|1883]])